* GF180MCU 3.3V FET models - typical corner (standalone)
* Extracted from: pdks/gf180mcuC/libs.tech/ngspice/sm141064.ngspice
* Compatible with ngspice 36
*
* Subcircuits accept w, l in MICROMETERS (matching glayout output convention)

* ── MIM Capacitor models (simplified ideal capacitors) ────────────────────
.subckt mimcap_1p0ff a b w=10 l=10
C0 a b 1p
.ends mimcap_1p0ff

.subckt mimcap_2p0ff a b w=10 l=10
C0 a b 2p
.ends mimcap_2p0ff

.subckt mimcap_p5ff a b w=10 l=10
C0 a b 0.5p
.ends mimcap_p5ff

.subckt mimcap a b w=10 l=10
C0 a b 1p
.ends mimcap

* Global parameters (from design.ngspice - typical, no Monte Carlo)
.param sw_stat_global=0 sw_stat_mismatch=0 mc_skew=3 fnoicor=0

* Noise corner parameters (fnoicor=0 = typical)
.param
+nfet_03v3_noia=3.2e+041
+nfet_03v3_noib=1.2e+020
+nfet_03v3_noic=6.0e+008
+pfet_03v3_noia=3.2e+041
+pfet_03v3_noib=1.8e+020
+pfet_03v3_noic=3.0e+009

* NFET 3.3V subcircuit - accepts w/l in micrometers
.subckt nfet_03v3 d g s b w=10 l=0.28 as=0 ad=0 ps=0 pd=0 nrd=0 nrs=0 par=1 dtemp=0 sa=0 sb=0 nf=1 sd=0 m=1
M0 d g s b nfet_03v3 W={w*1e-6} L={l*1e-6} AS=as AD=ad PS=ps PD=pd NRD=nrd NRS=nrs NF=nf SA=sa SB=sb SD=sd M=m
.ends nfet_03v3

