* PFET 3.3V subcircuit - accepts w/l in micrometers
.subckt pfet_03v3 d g s b w=10 l=0.28 as=0 ad=0 ps=0 pd=0 nrd=0 nrs=0 par=1 dtemp=0 sa=0 sb=0 nf=1 sd=0 m=1
M0 d g s b pfet_03v3 W={w*1e-6} L={l*1e-6} AS=as AD=ad PS=ps PD=pd NRD=nrd NRS=nrs NF=nf SA=sa SB=sb SD=sd M=m
.ends pfet_03v3

